{"tid":716081,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"HBO網站遭中國封鎖","createTime":"2018-06-25T03:35:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-28T00:03:37.000Z","uid":184679,"like":41,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"8e379a48c260b2f7ed70e52f887812e125ce176e","tid":716081,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T03:35:24.000Z","msg":"（法新社北京24日電） 美國電視台HBO脫口秀主持人約翰奧立佛近日在節目中嘲諷中國國家主席習近平，微博上相關討論已全遭刪除，<a href=\"http://據反審查團體GreatFire.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E6%93%9A%E5%8F%8D%E5%AF%A9%E6%9F%A5%E5%9C%98%E9%AB%94GreatFire.org&d=m%2FcvgakCNBeKT3vUml5W9f1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=dabf6071\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">據反審查團體GreatFire.org</a>表示，如今HBO網站也遭中國當局封鎖。<br />\n<br />\n約翰奧立佛（John Oliver）在單人脫口秀「上週今夜秀」（Last Week Tonight）17日節目開場時說：「中國是促進科技巨幅進步的國家，但他們似乎還做不到讓熊貓交配。」<br />\n<br />\n他表示，這些科技進步包括嚴苛的監視和審查措施。他還嘲諷中國審查員忙於刪除將習近平和維尼熊相比的訊息，被迫超時工作。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當法新社試圖在微博發表約翰奧立佛的名字時，網頁顯示「傳送失敗。內容違法！」<br />\n<br />\n除了YouTube和HBO，許多西方媒體網站都在中國遭封鎖，包括知名的臉書（Facebook）、推特（Twitter）和「紐約時報」（New York Times）。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Cr85Q0Cu72kpp3V4Z_KdFQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjMwO2g9NDIw/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-TW/homerun/afp.cnanews.gov.tw/6616637806cc32ea98ce41506fb948d1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FCr85Q0Cu72kpp3V4Z_KdFQ--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjMwO2g9NDIw%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-TW%2Fhomerun%2Fafp.cnanews.gov.tw%2F6616637806cc32ea98ce41506fb948d1&h=fa00119b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.yahoo.com/hbo%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99%E9%81%AD%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%B0%81%E9%8E%96-120502034.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.yahoo.com%2Fhbo%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E7%25AB%2599%25E9%2581%25AD%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25B0%2581%25E9%258E%2596-120502034.html&d=m%2FcvgakCNBeKT3vUml5W9f1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=179f6437\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.yahoo.com/hbo%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99%E9%81%AD%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%B0%81%E9%8E%96-120502034.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/27.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edfb0f881ea1fe11432815a70cfac2211262cc39","tid":716081,"uid":158301,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T03:38:31.000Z","msg":"終國成功令消滅互聯網足跡"},{"pid":"106ca060195eb7dd4a7c55b72d60f8f4499fb677","tid":716081,"uid":38904,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T03:41:20.000Z","msg":"john oliver成日玩命<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過佢嚟緊又笑支那架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利 有追開佢啲show"},{"pid":"98499b5cbfa3dc09ab0545a9cb6e9d0b17cc3ef2","tid":716081,"uid":152476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T03:43:11.000Z","msg":"好小器<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"131e7ed98e6257b090c2fb31063011c4674dc6cc","tid":716081,"uid":476,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T03:50:51.000Z","msg":"有邊個國家未比佢抽過水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 埃及個班都未驚 維尼驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2dad86c386c64032f834b54c1d20f1c6c086b9c1","tid":716081,"uid":171450,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T04:24:43.000Z","msg":"小器到呢"},{"pid":"c31f6e588e8dc69a0467cc77551887ad12308012","tid":716081,"uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T16:26:11.000Z","msg":"2025 2025 2025 2025⋯⋯"},{"pid":"9f0f540dfdd7b3f0492c7f8a7cedb44ec85d4427","tid":716081,"uid":135110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit